description: We are an established photography compan
overview:
We are an established photography company in San Diego and excel in delivering consistent results for every client. Whether it is for a Fortune 500 corporate event or an actor needing headshots, The Right Light Photography can address all your photographic needs.

With The Right Light Photography, we are: Thorough and professional in our process from beginning to end to include all requests from clients. Fully equipped with all equipment and staff to ensure full commitment and outcome. Accommodating to different events & headshots to create a custom experience with every client. Provide quality, unmatched service that form a relationship of trust with our clients.
